org.mybatis.generator.internal

类 JDBCConnectionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mybatis.generator.internal.JDBCConnectionFactory
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    ConnectionFactory

    public class JDBCConnectionFactory
extends Object
implements ConnectionFactory
    This class assumes that classes are cached elsewhere for performance reasons, but also to make sure that any native libraries are only loaded one time (avoids the dreaded UnsatisfiedLinkError library loaded in another classloader)
    作者:
    Jeff Butler

      • getConnection

        public Connection getConnection()
                         throws SQLException
        从接口复制的说明: ConnectionFactory
        Should return a connection to the database in use for this context. The generator will call this method only one time for each context. The generator will close the connection.
        指定者:
        getConnection 在接口中 ConnectionFactory
        返回:
        抛出:
        SQLException

      • addConfigurationProperties

        public void addConfigurationProperties(Properties properties)
        从接口复制的说明: ConnectionFactory
        Adds properties for this instance from any properties configured in the ConnectionFactory. This method will be called before any of the get methods.
        指定者:
        addConfigurationProperties 在接口中 ConnectionFactory
        参数:
        properties - All properties from the configuration
